episodes.title: The Kenyan Cult Leader Paul Mackenzie
episodes.description:
Leader of a doomsday cult in Kenya in which hundreds of people allegedly died from starvation has been charged with terrorism, radicalisation, and murder.

Paul Mackenzie and 94 others, including his wife, pleaded not guilty to all charges.

More than 400 bodies, including those of children, were exhumed from shallow graves on a piece of land said to be owned by the controversial preacher.

429 bodies have so far been autopsied. 52.2% are female 37.8% are male and 10% of the bodies were too badly decomposed to establish the gender.
